Class LangermannFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.LangermannFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FunctionIntf

    public class LangermannFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionIntf
    This class implements the Langermann Function in n-dimensions. The function is defined as follows: $$f(x) = \sum_{i=1}^m [c_i * exp(-||x-A_{(i)}||^2/π) * cos(π*||x-A_{(i)}||^2)]$$ (usually m=5) The argument boundaries are [0, 10]^n

    Title: popt4jlib

    Description: A Parallel Meta-Heuristic Optimization Library in Java
